    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Imagesize Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>imagesize</application> package analyzes image file headers
and returns the image size and DPI. It works with JPEG/JPEG
2000/PNG/GIF/TIFF/SVG/Netpbm/WebP formats.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

